<blockquote><h2><a name="Visual%20Indication%20Of%20Focus|">Visual Indication 
    of Focus</a></h2></blockquote>
<p>Visual Indication of Focus Includes: Text or Links, Image maps and Images, 
Image maps and images with non black and white background, Label and Control 
relationship. 
<table border>
    <tr>
        <td width="20%" valign="top" bgcolor="#FF9999"><h3><b>Visual Indication 
