            that panel header will have focus. (Tab to enter content of panel)<br> 
            <br> If the Sidebar is open but does not have focus then, the open 
            panel will header will have focus.<br> <br> If the Sidebar is open 
            and the open panel header has focus already the panels will collapse 
            with the top panel having focus.</td>
